You are here: Home  Services           Agro Infra and Food  Consulting






			
		Agro Infra & Food Consulting		





This division provides one stop solution to agriculture, livestock and food sectors. It plays a proactive role in mentoring, developing sustainable agri and food businesses. Government of India has given Food processing sector   a priority lending status. Ministry of Agriculture & Food Processing Industries, Govt. of India is encouraging private enterprises to set up units  in Food processing  by providing  grants, subsidies, soft  loans  while  APEDA  Facilitates export  of processed Food products again  by granting subsidies, training the exporters and providing market  assistance overseas. We provide our expertise to tap the upcoming opportunities and pave way for major investment in Food processing sector. 
Here is our Nine  Steps  Approach (Concept to Commissioning)


Identification of Potential Concept/Product


Preparation of Business Plan


Market Research for Backward & Forward Linkages


Location Identification and land  Acquisition




Project layout & other approvals


Commissioning


Project Completion


Trial runs & commencement of 
      Production 




Product Launch & Brand Creation





Spectrum of Services
Empanelled and Associated with
Projects Covered
Some of Our prestigious clients
Contact us



Market survey and research, Demand-Supply Studies based on Desk Research/Field Survey
Project/ Opportunity identification
Techno-Economic Feasibility Report (TEFR)
Assistance to project promoters in formation of SPV Company, finalization of project components and technology and assessment of technical viability
Preparation of pre-Feasibility  study  reports/ Project Proposals & Detailed Project Report(DPR)
Project Management Consultancy (PMC) and hand-holding services For  turnkey implementation of projects
Project appraisals  and Program Management Agency (PMA) services
Techno-economic appraisal of projects for financial sanction
Preparation  of Applications / Project Reports for Financial Grants From Govt. &  Liaison with Govt.Authorities to obtain financial sanctions
Assistance for  Certifications / Licenses / Accreditation

We  work with  Ministry of  Food  Processing Industries,Govt. of India,New  Delhi as Project Management Consultant  (PMC) for Infrastructure  Development  Schemes, viz. Mega  Food   Parks, integrated Cold  Chain, modernization of abattoirs, setting  up / up gradation of Quality Control  Laboratories / Food Testing Laboratories .
We have provided consultancy services to Mega Food Park Projects in Uttar Pradesh, Tamil Nadu, Maharashtra, Tripura, Gujarat, Madhya Pradesh and Sikkim for approval by the concerned Ministry of Food Processing Industries, Govt. of India, New Delhi. 
We have also prepared several reports on Integrated Cold Chain Projects, Food Testing Laboratories and Modernization of Abattoirs in Maharashtra, Sikkim, Manipur, Mizoram, Himachal Pradesh, Nagaland, Meghalaya etc. For more details, please visit our website www.mitconindia.com 

