HomeWebAdMiTBio_15@NetCUs2017-04-12T18:31:00+00:00 
MITCON Biopharma Has Over 3 Decades+ Experience And Counting
Making It The Most Trusted & Complete Biopharma Training And Consultancy Company Around In The Country.
 

Established in 1982, MITCON Consultancy and Engineering Services Ltd., is a joint venture of ICICI, SIDBI, IFCI, SICOM, MIDC, MSSIDC and Banks. Over almost three decades, MITCON has excelled in entrepreneurship development; by providing consultancy and training at affordable fees. MITCON’s training programs are industry relevant with curriculums continuously updated to include the latest. Our faculties are drawn from industry & academics. Several awards and appreciation from the industry, government agencies, stand testimony to the quality, sincerity and dedication of MITCON.
MITCON Biotechnology & Pharmaceutical Center is a Technology Business Incubator (TBI) supported by Department of Science & Technology (DST), Govt of India. The Center houses facility for Microbiology, Plant Tissue Culture, Biofertilizers, Genetic engineering, Fermentation Technology, Bioinformatics etc. MITCON’s Incubation center is located at Agriculture College Campus, Shivajinagar, Pune.
The   Center has various business activities with an objective to commercialize biotechnology like Training, Consultancy & Product Support. The Center offers various industry oriented Biotechnology & Clinical Research Training Courses


Best Training Programs & Business Consultancy : You Need It, We Gladly Provide It.
Our #1 priority is you, the user. We believe in our training programs and hold ourselves to the highest standards. We truly care about your business as much as you do, which is why we offer the best support around at our dedicated consultancy center. You can count on us.
