We’d Like to Hear From You, Get In Touch With Us!Established in 1982, MITCON Consultancy & Engineering Services Ltd, a joint venture of ICICI, SIDBI, IFCI, SICOM, MIDC, MSSIDC & Banks. Over past almost 3 decades, MITCON has excelled in entrepreneurship development, by providing consultancy & training at affordable fees. MITCON’s training programs are industry relevant with curriculums continuously updated to include the latest. Our facilities are drawn from industry and academics. Several awards & appreciation from the industry, government agencies, stand testimony to the quality, sincerity & dedication of MITCON.
MITCON Biotechnology & Pharmaceutical centre is a Technology Business Incubator (TBI) supported by Department of Science & Technology (DST), Government of India. The centre houses facility for Microbiology, Plant Tissue Culture, Biofertilizers, Genetic Engineering, Fermentation Technology, Bioinformatics etc. MITCON’s Incubation Centre is located at Agriculture College Campus, Shivajinagar, Pune. The centre has various business activities with an objective to commercialize biotechnology like training, Consultancy & Product support. Recently, we received an award for “The Best Incubator” from Villgro Foundation in Chennai. Establishment of MITCON-TBI has enabled many entrepreneurs to admit Technology development. MITCON has assisted more than 60 enterprises by now, generating employment for over 200 professionals through its incubation activity. MITCON has recently started loan assistance program for its incubatees though TDB, Govt. of India.
